      </accessrestrict>
      <arrangement id="aspace_92398a5fe9062f3160f9e0678423298f">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by topic.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_cbf9c4e9992fab50414cbcd016c453e6">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of photographs by James S. Hedden documenting the excavation and construction of Memorial Quadrangle at Yale. Other views include photographs of completed decorations and interiors, models, the installation of millstones and bells, assignment plans, and the construction of the fan vault ceiling in the Memorial Room of Harkness Tower.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
